title: Peach Hand Pies
description: These peach hand pies are next-level good! Made with a flaky, fool-proof, all-butter pie dough and filled with ripe peaches, goat cheese, plus a bit of green chile and basil, they ride the delicious line between savory and sweet. Continue reading Peach Hand Pies on 101 Cookbooks
author: Heidi Swanson
